                     <interp inst="t18000219-6-off27" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-6-off27" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000219-6-cd28" type="crimeDate">1st of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-6-off27 t18000219-6-cd28"></join>, a yard and a half of muslin, value 7s. the property of 
                     
